{"type":"text","timestamp":1781756144139,"sessionID":"ses_1270ff7ffffeghChHIr0qZoieH","part":{"id":"prt_ed8f1299c001vGLFDfxi3uYa2j","messageID":"msg_ed8f1175d001uByI9N17QE5KN6","sessionID":"ses_1270ff7ffffeghChHIr0qZoieH","type":"text","text":"The workflow confirms this is the single-executor lineage path with an overridden `artifact_dir`; I will not run the resolver or stage artifacts, because both would touch paths outside the lineage scope or violate the user override.","time":{"start":1781756144028,"end":1781756144138},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d47d29faa72370f016a3370f002108191b4ae6037ffde0691","phase":"commentary"}}}}
